{"word":"παρέξειμι","slug":"παρέξειμι","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>παρέξειμι</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:εἶμι'><el>εἶμι</el></a> <i>ibo</i>\n<el>(<a href='S:infinitive'>inf.</a> <el>-εξιέναι</el>) </el><p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>to go out beside, pass by</i> or <i>alongside of</i>, <a href='S:cum'>c.</a> <a href='S:accusative'>acc.</a> loci, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b>: <a href='S:absolute, absolutely'>absol.</a>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Euripides'>Eur.</a></b>, <a href='S:et cetera'>etc.</a><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><i>to turn aside out of the path</i>, <b><a href='S:Plato'>Plat.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><i>to overstep, transgress</i>, <b><a href='S:Aeschylus'>Aesch.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Sophocles'>Soph.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}